<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
      Learn. Document. Share.
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">
      Live well in a world<br />of <span class="gold">broken money.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      The old playbook is done. AI is rewriting the rules. Bitcoin is rewriting the money. 
      And the builders who move now — before the crowd catches on — will own the next decade.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Richer Living is a real-time documentation of a complete life rebuild. 
      No gurus. No hype. Just a framework that works — and a founder living it in public.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Get The Weekly Brief — Free</a>
      <a href="#levers" class="btn btn-outline">See The Framework</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-levers">
      <div class="lever-pill">Conscious Silicon</div>
      <div class="lever-pill">Long Value</div>
      <div class="lever-pill">Short Fiat</div>
      <div class="lever-pill">Longevity</div>
      <div class="lever-pill">Income Engines</div>
      <div class="lever-pill">Geo-Arbitrage</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-levers {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .lever-pill {
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 4rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-levers {
      justify-content: center;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
